## Step 8 — Ongoing Habits

### Weekly (5-10 min)
- [ ] Export any new/updated workflows to `Workflows/Exports/`
- [ ] `git pull` to get teammates' changes
- [ ] Commit and push your changes

### After an Incident
- [ ] Create `Operations/Incidents/YYYY-MM-DD_Brief-Description.md`
- [ ] Include: what happened, impact, timeline, root cause, resolution, prevention
- [ ] Commit and push

### After Infrastructure Changes
- [ ] Create `Operations/Change-Log/YYYY-MM-DD_Brief-Description.md`
- [ ] Update any affected docs in `Docs/`
- [ ] Commit and push

